(Republished)

Samuel Atkin et al., Appellants, v. Hill, Darlington & Grimm et al., Respondents.

Judgment dismissing the complaint affirmed, with $25 costs to the respondents. Opinion Per Curiam. Concur — Rabin, McNally and Steuer, JJ.; Botein, P. J., and Eager, J., dissent in an opinion by Eager, J. The order of this court entered on June 17, 1965, is vacated. [See 23 A D 2d 331.]
